1
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:35,079
Division Commander, we're just waiting for your order.

2
00:01:35,079 --> 00:01:36,000
We'll launch a full-scale attack immediately.

3
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,200
And wipe out that guy named Wei.

4
00:01:37,439 --> 00:01:38,519
Don't be so rash.

5
00:01:38,760 --> 00:01:40,200
He dared to hijack our munitions.

6
00:01:40,599 --> 00:01:41,599
He's so carried away with himself.

7
00:01:41,599 --> 00:01:43,319
How can we just give him a warning?

8
00:01:44,239 --> 00:01:46,439
Although Commander Wei's strength is not worth mentioning,

9
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:49,000
his existence must have its reason.

10
00:01:51,079 --> 00:01:53,480
He is a pawn that Chen uses to check me.

11
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:54,439
If Division Commander Chen finds out

12
00:01:54,439 --> 00:01:55,799
that I'm attacking Commander Wei with full force,

13
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:57,760
won't he send reinforcements?

14
00:01:58,640 --> 00:01:59,400
Report!

15
00:02:02,079 --> 00:02:02,879
Telegram received.

16
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:04,439
Commander Wei's youngest uncle has died.

17
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,680
He died at quite a convenient time.

18
00:02:31,199 --> 00:02:32,039
My condolences.

19
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:34,120
It's very kind of you, Commander Liao.

20
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:35,879
Please.

21
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:44,800
I heard Commander Liao plans to send troops against me.

22
00:02:46,199 --> 00:02:48,039
No fighting during planting or harvesting.

23
00:02:48,159 --> 00:02:49,439
No fighting during festivals or holidays.

24
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:51,039
No fighting in the crop fields.

25
00:02:51,159 --> 00:02:52,680
No fighting during weddings or funerals.

26
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,879
Sending troops now would be unethical.

27
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,400
Rest assured.

28
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,800
We all understand the Four No-Fight Rules.

29
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,800
Our Division Commander won't take advantage of misfortune.

30
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:04,879
Once the old gentleman is buried,

31
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,159
look,

32
00:03:06,919 --> 00:03:08,199
should I continue to send troops,

33
00:03:08,319 --> 00:03:09,759
or will you return my things to me?

34
00:03:11,039 --> 00:03:11,919
Commander Liao,

35
00:03:12,319 --> 00:03:13,840
there might be a misunderstanding here.

36
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:16,120
I fell into that Division Commander Chen's trap.

37
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:18,960
That Colonel under me, Fan Pengju,

38
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:19,960
used my banner

39
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,240
to hijack your munitions.

40
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:23,199
In the end, he handed it all over to Division Commander Chen.

41
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,240
He even became a Brigade Commander over there.

42
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,080
You see,

43
00:03:26,439 --> 00:03:28,479
this was clearly planned, a conspiracy.

44
00:03:28,479 --> 00:03:29,759
They were in cahoots long ago.

45
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,120
I also received news.

46
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:36,199
I heard that fat son of yours

47
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:38,400
is now in Division Commander Chen's hands.

48
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,919
I wouldn't joke about such things.

49
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,080
It is absolutely true.

50
00:03:47,039 --> 00:03:48,479
Always causing me trouble.

51
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:51,919
If Commander Liao wants to send troops,

52
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:54,560
I am willing to lend you a hand.

53
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,639
That fellow Chen

54
00:03:58,639 --> 00:04:00,360
made me offend you for no reason.

55
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,960
I lost a regiment,

56
00:04:02,759 --> 00:04:04,280
and took the blame for such a big mess.

57
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,240
This anger,

58
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,520
I cannot swallow it.

59
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:10,479
Then wait for my military order.

60
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:16,800
So we're allied with Commander Liao now?

61
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,360
So we're going to ally with Commander Wei?

62
00:04:20,199 --> 00:04:22,079
I don't need his few weak soldiers.

63
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:26,199
Telling me to wait for his military order...

64
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,360
Is he treating me as an ally,

65
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:31,680
or treating me like his foot soldier?

66
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:40,279
Your Old man knows you're here,

67
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:43,480
and sent troops to attack Division Commander Chen to save you.

68
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:44,759
How many men did he send?

69
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,439
Is it the entire army?

70
00:04:47,399 --> 00:04:48,800
I don't know that yet.

71
00:04:48,959 --> 00:04:50,279
If it's not the entire army,

72
00:04:51,199 --> 00:04:52,879
then it's not necessarily to save me.

73
00:04:53,399 --> 00:04:56,199
He and Division Commander Chen have always been at odds.

74
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:03,000
When your Old man sends troops,

75
00:05:03,519 --> 00:05:05,040
Division Commander Chen will send me

76
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,560
to launch a surprise attack on his base.

77
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,240
You'll come with me then.

78
00:05:09,079 --> 00:05:09,920
Where are we going?

79
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:12,399
I'll take a detour to intercept Commander Liao,

80
00:05:13,319 --> 00:05:14,439
and return you to him.

81
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:16,319
That way, we can avoid a battle.

82
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,720
Let them fight.

83
00:05:18,399 --> 00:05:19,480
I want to see

84
00:05:20,079 --> 00:05:21,720
if he's really coming to save me.

85
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:30,800
You know many people die in a battle.

86
00:05:31,639 --> 00:05:32,920
If I return you,

87
00:05:33,759 --> 00:05:36,360
your father won't have a reason to send troops.

88
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:39,079
You're even more naive than I am.

89
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,319
If Division Commander Chen didn't want to fight,

90
00:05:41,759 --> 00:05:43,439
he would have sent me back himself.

91
00:05:43,959 --> 00:05:46,000
Would he need you to worry about it here?

92
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,360
You...

93
00:05:50,199 --> 00:05:51,879
aren't you worried about your Old man at all?

94
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:56,120
I still have that much confidence in him.

95
00:05:59,839 --> 00:06:01,160
He's good at fighting.

96
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:14,120
Reporting, Division Commander.

97
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,120
Commander Wei says...

98
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,600
just when his youngest uncle was about to be buried,

99
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:18,000
they found the feng shui of the ancestral grave had changed.

100
00:06:18,199 --> 00:06:19,160
They have to relocate the grave.

101
00:06:19,319 --> 00:06:20,519
So he won't be coming here to meet up.

102
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:21,839
He said he will lead his troops

103
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:22,959
to support us on the battlefield.

104
00:06:24,319 --> 00:06:25,240
Continue reconnaissance.

105
00:06:26,439 --> 00:06:28,079
Support, my ass.

106
00:06:28,519 --> 00:06:30,399
He clearly just wants a free ride.

107
00:06:30,879 --> 00:06:32,279
I never counted on him anyway.

108
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,600
I'm deploying the whole army.

109
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,600
The plan is to finish off Chen's forces first,

110
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,839
then swallow up Wei's forces directly.

111
00:06:37,639 --> 00:06:38,879
It doesn't matter if he comes or not.

112
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:40,759
Move out.

113
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:41,879
Yes, sir.

114
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:43,360
How is it?

115
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,079
Nothing, nothing.

116
00:06:44,519 --> 00:06:45,680
There's not a single person.

117
00:06:46,199 --> 00:06:47,120
Did you look clearly?

118
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:48,360
How about you?

119
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:48,959
None.

120
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,279
Let's go.

121
00:06:50,959 --> 00:06:51,720
Big Brother.

122
00:06:51,879 --> 00:06:53,160
Not even a ghost's shadow.

123
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:53,879
Come in, quick.

124
00:06:53,879 --> 00:06:55,000
It's very safe.

125
00:06:58,279 --> 00:06:59,560
They've turned out in full force.

126
00:07:00,439 --> 00:07:01,600
Gone to fight for their lives.

127
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:04,279
And he said his Old man didn't care about him.

128
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,439
Hurry up.

129
00:07:05,439 --> 00:07:07,279
This is too abnormal. Don't go in yet.

130
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:08,399
It's fine.

131
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:10,959
We completed the mission without wasting a single soldier.

132
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:13,160
Division Commander, are we really going to fight?

133
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,439
He betrayed me so easily.

134
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,040
We must do what is necessary.

135
00:07:18,839 --> 00:07:19,920
Teach him a lesson.

136
00:07:20,759 --> 00:07:21,560
Alright.

137
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:39,759
Who's there?

138
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,120
Scarface.

139
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,920
Prepare to counterattack.

140
00:07:52,199 --> 00:07:52,959
What?

141
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:55,480
Prepare to counterattack.

142
00:07:56,319 --> 00:07:57,560
I can't hear you.

143
00:07:58,879 --> 00:08:00,079
I told you not to come in.

144
00:08:00,279 --> 00:08:01,519
Now we're trapped like dogs.

145
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,240
Shut your jinxed mouth.

146
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,680
It definitely wasn't Commander Liao.

147
00:08:06,199 --> 00:08:08,160
No matter who is ambushing me...

148
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,160
Xuanjizi.

149
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,519
Prepare to counterattack.

150
00:08:11,639 --> 00:08:12,720
Prepare to counterattack.

151
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,680
Brigade Commander Fan.

152
00:08:17,079 --> 00:08:18,160
It's me.

153
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:19,600
Misunderstanding.

154
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,240
Don't shoot.

155
00:08:22,399 --> 00:08:23,759
Is that Commander Wei?

156
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:24,959
That's right.

157
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,040
I thought you were Commander Liao.

158
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:32,279
You're here to fight Commander Liao?

159
00:08:32,399 --> 00:08:33,439
Yes.

160
00:08:33,680 --> 00:08:36,600
Aren't you allied with Commander Liao?

161
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:38,960
That was me and Division Commander Chen...

162
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,480
...putting out false information.

163
00:08:40,759 --> 00:08:43,000
Division Commander Chen is my real ally.

164
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:45,120
The two of us are partners.

165
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,799
Darn it.

166
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:08,840
Stop the attack.

167
00:09:19,879 --> 00:09:22,080
Division Commander, there might be an ambush.

168
00:09:24,919 --> 00:09:27,639
Division Commander Chen, you old turtle.

169
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,519
Still hiding?

170
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:38,559
This battle is a guaranteed victory.

171
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,960
No need to trouble our Division Commander Chen.

172
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,759
Who the hell are you?

173
00:09:44,039 --> 00:09:45,320
My surname is Huo.

174
00:09:45,759 --> 00:09:47,279
I am Division Commander Chen's Staff Officer.

175
00:09:47,759 --> 00:09:49,600
Once we defeat Commander Liao,

176
00:09:49,879 --> 00:09:52,759
this will be the battle that makes my name.

177
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:54,480
A mere Staff Officer.

178
00:09:54,799 --> 00:09:56,120
Such big talk.

179
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,559
Whether the talk is big or not,

180
00:09:57,799 --> 00:09:59,519
try me and you'll find out.

181
00:10:08,799 --> 00:10:09,600
Hoist him up.

182
00:10:13,159 --> 00:10:14,039
Yes, Young Master.

183
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:15,960
Don't panic.

184
00:10:19,399 --> 00:10:20,120
Shout.

185
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,360
Shout.

186
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:27,600
Who told you to shout 'Ouch'?

187
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:29,000
Told you to shout for your Old man to come save you.

188
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:32,120
Old man, come save me!

189
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:33,960
Save me!

190
00:10:36,559 --> 00:10:37,600
Why don't we take a gamble?

191
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:40,120
I cannot gamble with my soldiers' lives.

192
00:10:40,279 --> 00:10:41,360
Even if there is an ambush,

193
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:42,559
give me one company,

194
00:10:42,679 --> 00:10:44,080
and I'll pile up bodies to get in.

195
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:45,720
All forces, fall back one li.

196
00:10:45,879 --> 00:10:46,480
Set up camp.

197
00:10:47,639 --> 00:10:48,480
That son of a bitch.

198
00:10:49,039 --> 00:10:50,639
Using my son as bait.

199
00:10:50,759 --> 00:10:52,080
It's simply despicable.

200
00:10:53,399 --> 00:10:53,960
Retreat.

201
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:55,399
Yes, sir.

202
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,879
Commander Liao is a coward too.

203
00:11:04,519 --> 00:11:05,759
He's giving up on you just like that.

204
00:11:06,399 --> 00:11:09,559
You guys should negotiate, just go through the motions.

205
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:12,159
At least tell him not to hit me.

206
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:13,919
It hurts so much.

207
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:17,960
I'm not afraid of dying, I'm just afraid of pain!

208
00:11:24,039 --> 00:11:25,639
Brother Fan took my munitions

209
00:11:25,639 --> 00:11:27,200
and went to join Division Commander Chen.

210
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,639
Your betrayal

211
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:30,480
was to make Commander Liao believe

212
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:32,399
that the alliance between Division Commander Chen and me

213
00:11:32,519 --> 00:11:33,759
was at a crucial breaking point.

214
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:35,519
So, you actually deserve credit.

215
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,120
I was thinking,

216
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:42,279
if Brother Fan had been loyal to me back then,

217
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,360
and refused to steal the munitions,

218
00:11:45,039 --> 00:11:46,720
I really wouldn't have known what to do.

219
00:11:47,039 --> 00:11:48,360
I also took to heart

220
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:50,080
Commander Wei's teachings.

221
00:11:51,039 --> 00:11:52,159
Once you put on the uniform,

222
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,639
there is no more brotherhood.

223
00:11:54,919 --> 00:11:55,679
I know.

224
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:57,240
This time Division Commander Chen sent you

225
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:58,799
to raid Commander Liao's base.

226
00:11:59,159 --> 00:12:01,000
I was afraid Commander Liao might have a backup plan.

227
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,200
That is why

228
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:03,679
I specifically called my brothers

229
00:12:03,919 --> 00:12:05,519
to come and lend you a hand.

230
00:12:07,759 --> 00:12:08,879
Thank you, Commander Wei.

231
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:11,240
You and I are brothers, brothers for life.

232
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:12,360
No need to be polite.

233
00:12:13,159 --> 00:12:14,000
Commander Wei, when

234
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:15,960
you couldn't distinguish friend from foe,

235
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,200
you rashly opened fire.

236
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,639
Wasn't that a bit too reckless?

237
00:12:18,879 --> 00:12:20,000
Xuanjizi.

238
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:23,200
You have the nerve to stand up and lecture me?

239
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,600
You are the one who disappointed me the most.

240
00:12:27,879 --> 00:12:29,519
Commander Wei, as a general,

241
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:31,159
if you want to win people's hearts,

242
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:34,320
you need to show some real skill.

243
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:36,720
Rebels are rebels.

244
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:38,039
And you think you're justified?

245
00:12:38,519 --> 00:12:39,399
Alright, alright.

246
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:40,799
Everyone stop arguing.

247
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:42,519
We are allies again now.

248
00:12:43,039 --> 00:12:44,879
My rank is the same as Division Commander Chen's.

249
00:12:45,399 --> 00:12:47,480
Now Brother Fan must follow my command.

250
00:12:47,759 --> 00:12:49,600
I presume Commander Liao and Division Commander Chen

251
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,600
have already engaged in battle.

252
00:12:51,159 --> 00:12:52,200
I now order

253
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,159
Brigade Commander Fan,

254
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:56,159
lead your troops,

255
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,440
march at double speed,

256
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:59,519
and reinforce Division Commander Chen.

257
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:17,159
You just retreated like that?

258
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:18,399
Division Commander

259
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:19,960
That Commander Liao

260
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:21,399
he is a cunning old fox.

261
00:13:21,519 --> 00:13:22,679
We used his son as bait

262
00:13:22,679 --> 00:13:23,639
but he didn't fall for it.

263
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:27,039
You tie a child up on the battlefield

264
00:13:30,879 --> 00:13:32,840
isn't he just our bargaining chip?

265
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:36,000
He can be our hostage

266
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:37,720
but you can't let a child

267
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:38,639
go block the muzzle.

268
00:13:38,639 --> 00:13:39,159
Yes, sir.

269
00:13:48,759 --> 00:13:49,720
At that time, Liao's army

270
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:51,039
didn't enter the ambush circle.

271
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:52,679
And my reinforcements hadn't arrived.

272
00:13:52,879 --> 00:13:54,720
If we had acted rashly,

273
00:13:55,159 --> 00:13:57,519
I fear it would have been a senseless sacrifice.

274
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:58,639
Exactly.

275
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:00,919
Then what if Liao's army attacks now?

276
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:02,360
Don't worry, Division Commander.

277
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:04,759
If one plan fails, we have another.

278
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:11,039
What did you call us here for?

279
00:14:11,559 --> 00:14:13,080
I haven't even fed my chickens at home.

280
00:14:13,679 --> 00:14:15,360
We aren't soldiers.

281
00:14:16,039 --> 00:14:17,840
Why call us to the battlefield?

282
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:18,600
That's right.

283
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:20,000
There won't be bullets flying, right?

284
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:21,159
Stop talking, move faster.

285
00:14:22,519 --> 00:14:23,519
What is going on here?

286
00:14:24,679 --> 00:14:25,320
Hurry up.

287
00:14:25,480 --> 00:14:27,519
To resist Liao's army, we're reinforcing fortifications.

288
00:14:29,879 --> 00:14:31,399
First a little child,

289
00:14:31,919 --> 00:14:33,200
now common folk.

290
00:14:33,679 --> 00:14:34,519
Staff Officer Huo

291
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:37,360
you really have opened my eyes.

292
00:14:38,159 --> 00:14:38,840
I know

293
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:41,960
this doesn't fit Division Commander Chen's usual style.

294
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:45,559
But what if Commander Liao doesn't care?

295
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:46,840
What do we do then?

296
00:14:47,039 --> 00:14:47,840
Then that's perfect.

297
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:49,759
Using their lives

298
00:14:50,480 --> 00:14:52,679
will add to Commander Liao's crimes.

299
00:14:55,039 --> 00:14:56,600
If Division Commander Chen has a better way,

300
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:58,279
your subordinate will certainly obey.

301
00:15:01,519 --> 00:15:02,320
Staff Officer Huo

302
00:15:03,759 --> 00:15:04,799
thank you for your trouble.

303
00:15:08,399 --> 00:15:09,440
This guy named Huo

304
00:15:09,440 --> 00:15:10,960
is simply unfit to be a soldier.

305
00:15:13,039 --> 00:15:13,840
Division Commander

306
00:15:15,039 --> 00:15:17,320
Sacrifice on the battlefield is inevitable.

307
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:19,080
You can't bear to sacrifice soldiers,

308
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:20,679
you can't bear to sacrifice civilians.

309
00:15:21,039 --> 00:15:22,600
Then are you willing to sacrifice the Young Master?

310
00:15:23,919 --> 00:15:25,519
If we can't find a breakthrough, we wait.

311
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:27,200
Wait for the opponent to make a mistake first.

312
00:15:27,399 --> 00:15:28,279
Report!

313
00:15:28,799 --> 00:15:31,360
Wei's vanguard is one kilometer behind us.

314
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:33,360
The allied forces have arrived.

315
00:15:33,440 --> 00:15:34,360
Report!

316
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:36,559
Wei's army has stopped marching.

317
00:15:36,799 --> 00:15:37,399
At our army's

318
00:15:37,399 --> 00:15:39,320
return route, they are building fortifications.

319
00:15:40,559 --> 00:15:41,799
Something's wrong.

320
00:15:42,519 --> 00:15:44,039
They've sandwiched us in the middle.

321
00:15:47,879 --> 00:15:49,759
I never expected him to help anyway.

322
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:52,320
I didn't expect him to turn the tables on me.

323
00:15:54,159 --> 00:15:55,000
I was careless.

324
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:56,519
Commander Liao

325
00:15:58,559 --> 00:15:59,840
Commander Liao

326
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:04,480
Commander Liao

327
00:16:04,679 --> 00:16:06,559
I've arrived so late,

328
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,600
yet you've made no progress at all.

329
00:16:08,919 --> 00:16:10,360
I thought you were so formidable.

330
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:12,519
It's simply too disappointing.

331
00:16:14,360 --> 00:16:15,960
I fell for your trap, I admit it.

332
00:16:16,559 --> 00:16:18,360
Would you do me the honor of speaking at the front?

333
00:16:18,639 --> 00:16:20,639
Still talking tough.

334
00:16:21,120 --> 00:16:22,720
Let's see what tricks you're playing.

335
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:30,759
Brigade Commander Fan

336
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:33,720
I always think of you when there's something good.

337
00:16:33,799 --> 00:16:35,240
Come on, let's go together.

338
00:16:37,360 --> 00:16:38,879
Father and son soldiers in battle,

339
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,600
brothers by blood in a fight.

340
00:16:42,919 --> 00:16:43,799
Scarface

341
00:16:58,679 --> 00:16:59,519
Commander Liao

342
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:01,919
The situation is already very clear.

343
00:17:02,399 --> 00:17:04,639
As the saying goes, a wise man submits to circumstances.

344
00:17:05,279 --> 00:17:07,080
You shouldn't fight a lone battle,

345
00:17:07,399 --> 00:17:08,840
stubbornly holding out here.

346
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:10,680
Although we belong to different camps,

347
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:13,440
we agreed beforehand never to harm the innocent.

348
00:17:14,039 --> 00:17:14,960
This has also been the tacit understanding

349
00:17:14,960 --> 00:17:16,319
between our three armies all along.

350
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:18,759
Commander Chen's army exploits the weak, violating our principles.

351
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:22,000
I hope you won't associate with his kind.

352
00:17:22,319 --> 00:17:23,279
The weak?

353
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:25,000
What does that mean?

354
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:26,759
Why don't I understand?

355
00:17:27,039 --> 00:17:28,839
Division Commander Chen used our Young Master as bait

356
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:30,400
and used civilians as human shields.

357
00:17:31,000 --> 00:17:31,799
If that weren't the case,

358
00:17:32,599 --> 00:17:33,799
how could he be a match for us?

359
00:17:36,279 --> 00:17:37,839
Acting like this

360
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:40,039
is worse than bandits.

361
00:17:40,839 --> 00:17:41,640
Commander Wei,

362
00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:43,400
I'll give you two choices.

363
00:17:43,680 --> 00:17:44,960
Either join forces with me,

364
00:17:45,359 --> 00:17:47,640
or go convince Division Commander Chen.

365
00:17:47,799 --> 00:17:49,480
After releasing my son and evacuating the civilians,

366
00:17:49,480 --> 00:17:50,440
however you want to fight,

367
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:52,000
I, Liao, will fight you to the end.

368
00:17:52,079 --> 00:17:52,799
I agree.

369
00:17:53,160 --> 00:17:54,359
What do you mean you agree?

370
00:17:54,960 --> 00:17:56,400
No matter which one you choose,

371
00:17:56,839 --> 00:17:58,519
you can't harm the innocent.

372
00:17:59,480 --> 00:18:00,400
In war,

373
00:18:00,680 --> 00:18:01,519
to win,

374
00:18:01,799 --> 00:18:04,079
using some stratagems is quite normal.

375
00:18:04,680 --> 00:18:06,200
Not all stratagems in the art of war

376
00:18:06,279 --> 00:18:07,920
are gentlemanly tactics.

377
00:18:09,519 --> 00:18:11,319
It seems your Chen and Wei armies

378
00:18:11,319 --> 00:18:12,759
really are two of a kind,

379
00:18:13,039 --> 00:18:14,240
sharing the same vile ambitions.

380
00:18:15,799 --> 00:18:16,799
Commander Liao,

381
00:18:17,119 --> 00:18:18,519
if you can't win the battle,

382
00:18:18,759 --> 00:18:21,440
don't stand there sourly talking nonsense.

383
00:18:29,720 --> 00:18:30,519
I...

384
00:18:30,799 --> 00:18:32,000
have a suggestion.

385
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:35,039
Let's all sit down,

386
00:18:35,039 --> 00:18:36,440
have some hotpot,

387
00:18:36,599 --> 00:18:37,559
play some mahjong,

388
00:18:37,759 --> 00:18:38,960
and get together

389
00:18:39,559 --> 00:18:41,200
to talk this out clearly. How about it?

390
00:18:41,839 --> 00:18:42,960
Like hell we will!

391
00:18:43,279 --> 00:18:45,200
We finally have a bit of an advantage.

392
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:47,400
Whose side are you on right now?

393
00:18:47,799 --> 00:18:49,759
I stand on the side of justice.

394
00:18:50,039 --> 00:18:51,119
Fighting wars, you know,

395
00:18:51,319 --> 00:18:52,359
wastes money and hurts the people.

396
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:54,640
If we can avoid it, we should.

397
00:18:55,559 --> 00:18:56,799
Avoid it my ass!

398
00:18:57,240 --> 00:18:58,160
What we need right now

399
00:18:58,160 --> 00:18:59,680
is the momentum to pursue victory.

400
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:01,240
And here you are deflating morale.

401
00:19:01,519 --> 00:19:03,880
Watch out or I'll charge you with shaking military morale.

402
00:19:06,119 --> 00:19:08,680
Do you really think I'm your soldier?

403
00:19:09,359 --> 00:19:10,640
You need to get this straight.

404
00:19:11,119 --> 00:19:13,319
I looked down on you back then,

405
00:19:13,319 --> 00:19:14,240
that's why I left.

406
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:17,119
You disobeyed military orders and defected in battle!

407
00:19:17,119 --> 00:19:17,559
I...

408
00:19:17,559 --> 00:19:18,240
Don't move!

409
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:19,359
Put them down!

410
00:19:24,279 --> 00:19:25,079
Wei,

411
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:27,319
I've been waiting for this moment for a long time.

412
00:19:28,359 --> 00:19:29,720
I disobeyed military orders?

413
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:31,359
My brothers,

414
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:33,880
are you going to disobey my military orders too?

415
00:19:35,039 --> 00:19:36,039
Let me tell you,

416
00:19:37,319 --> 00:19:39,039
we two are sworn brothers.

417
00:19:39,279 --> 00:19:40,640
Commander Liao's son

418
00:19:41,039 --> 00:19:42,799
is also my sworn brother.

419
00:19:43,599 --> 00:19:44,680
His old man

420
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:46,720
is our old man too.

421
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:49,519
Old man,

422
00:19:50,079 --> 00:19:51,160
please trust me.

423
00:20:00,559 --> 00:20:01,240
Fine.

424
00:20:02,240 --> 00:20:03,440
I'll take this gamble.

425
00:20:04,599 --> 00:20:05,880
Big Brother, please.

426
00:20:06,640 --> 00:20:07,920
Commanders, please.

427
00:20:22,440 --> 00:20:24,079
Aren't we here to talk business?

428
00:20:24,519 --> 00:20:26,799
Why come to such a seedy place?

429
00:20:30,839 --> 00:20:32,920
Welcome, gentlemen! Welcome, welcome!

430
00:20:34,960 --> 00:20:37,039
Boss Wei, you haven't been here in a long time.

431
00:20:37,039 --> 00:20:39,000
Are you opening that bottle of yours today?

432
00:20:39,119 --> 00:20:39,839
You've got the wrong person.

433
00:20:39,839 --> 00:20:41,079
I've never even been here.

434
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:43,079
Girls!

435
00:20:43,599 --> 00:20:45,359
Hello, gentlemen.

436
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:46,839
My name is Straw Mushroom.

437
00:20:47,039 --> 00:20:48,400
My name is Bamboo Mushroom.

438
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:49,680
My name is Shiitake.

439
00:20:49,680 --> 00:20:51,680
My name is Termite Mushroom.

440
00:20:51,920 --> 00:20:53,519
Commander Liao, pick one.

441
00:20:55,279 --> 00:20:56,240
No, no.

442
00:20:57,079 --> 00:20:57,920
Division Commander Chen.

443
00:21:02,759 --> 00:21:03,799
Commander Wei.

444
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:10,200
It seems they aren't satisfied.

445
00:21:10,920 --> 00:21:11,720
Bring in the next batch.

446
00:21:13,119 --> 00:21:15,240
Have fun, gentlemen.

447
00:21:16,960 --> 00:21:17,680
Hurry up now.

448
00:21:18,039 --> 00:21:19,200
Here, here, here.

449
00:21:20,240 --> 00:21:21,480
Come on, brother, have a drink.

450
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:24,559
For you, for you.

451
00:21:24,559 --> 00:21:27,000
Treating us to wine and women at a time like this?

452
00:21:27,279 --> 00:21:28,160
It's inappropriate.

453
00:21:29,119 --> 00:21:30,000
Indeed.

454
00:21:30,200 --> 00:21:31,720
We are at war with each other.

455
00:21:31,960 --> 00:21:33,119
Pulling these stunts...

456
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:35,480
...is simply treating it like a joke.

457
00:21:37,039 --> 00:21:38,079
Holding girls...

458
00:21:38,599 --> 00:21:40,720
...is surely better than holding guns while talking.

459
00:21:40,920 --> 00:21:42,000
Exactly.

460
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:42,839
Brigade Commander Fan.

461
00:21:43,079 --> 00:21:44,960
What gives you the right to arrange things for the Division Commanders?

462
00:21:45,480 --> 00:21:47,519
Have you forgotten your own status?

463
00:21:49,319 --> 00:21:50,000
Fine.

464
00:21:50,400 --> 00:21:53,599
Today I'll speak with the status of a "half".

465
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:54,960
To say a few words.

466
00:21:59,599 --> 00:22:00,960
Right now, it's...

467
00:22:01,160 --> 00:22:03,119
...you two plus my half...

468
00:22:03,680 --> 00:22:06,000
...attacking this one together.

469
00:22:07,240 --> 00:22:08,119
This one...

470
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:10,359
...is just meat on the chopping block.

471
00:22:10,720 --> 00:22:11,799
At the mercy of others.

472
00:22:13,240 --> 00:22:14,240
But today...

473
00:22:14,759 --> 00:22:17,240
...I've recognized this one as my Old man.

474
00:22:18,319 --> 00:22:21,119
According to ethics, according to custom...

475
00:22:21,119 --> 00:22:22,440
According to anything...

476
00:22:22,960 --> 00:22:24,799
...how can a son go and beat up his Old man?

477
00:22:24,960 --> 00:22:26,359
Then you can withdraw.

478
00:22:26,359 --> 00:22:28,000
It won't make much difference anyway.

479
00:22:29,039 --> 00:22:30,240
After I withdraw...

480
00:22:30,319 --> 00:22:31,599
...I plan to attack you.

481
00:22:34,839 --> 00:22:35,720
Why?

482
00:22:36,519 --> 00:22:37,480
In a fight...

483
00:22:39,359 --> 00:22:40,599
...there must be fairness.

484
00:22:41,160 --> 00:22:42,400
Two against one...

485
00:22:43,960 --> 00:22:45,200
...is just bullying.

486
00:22:46,359 --> 00:22:48,119
How about this, Division Commander Chen...

487
00:22:48,400 --> 00:22:50,359
...you and Commander Liao fight it out.

488
00:22:52,039 --> 00:22:52,920
My half...

489
00:22:53,440 --> 00:22:55,240
...will fight against you.

490
00:22:57,039 --> 00:22:58,480
I won't be afraid of you either.

491
00:22:58,839 --> 00:22:59,519
We...

492
00:22:59,839 --> 00:23:01,640
...won't interfere with each other.

493
00:23:02,400 --> 00:23:03,759
Then what the hell are we fighting for?

494
00:23:04,599 --> 00:23:06,119
These soldiers...

495
00:23:06,519 --> 00:23:09,000
...are all raised by ourselves.

496
00:23:10,279 --> 00:23:12,759
Who would be willing to let...

497
00:23:13,039 --> 00:23:15,319
...their own soldiers die for nothing?

498
00:23:15,920 --> 00:23:17,240
I mainly want...

499
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:19,200
...to use the minimum loss...

500
00:23:19,359 --> 00:23:20,640
...to let the three Division Commanders...

501
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:23,200
...turn hostility into friendship.

502
00:23:23,400 --> 00:23:26,240
Dogs are raised to guard doors, soldiers are raised to fight wars.

503
00:23:27,240 --> 00:23:29,759
Once a soldier, one must be prepared to sacrifice.

504
00:23:29,920 --> 00:23:31,839
If they die on the battlefield...

505
00:23:31,839 --> 00:23:33,200
...that's just their tough luck.

506
00:23:39,119 --> 00:23:40,160
Tell me,

507
00:23:40,440 --> 00:23:42,319
how can we reduce losses

508
00:23:43,359 --> 00:23:44,759
and still determine a winner?

509
00:23:45,200 --> 00:23:47,440
Like eating noodles with one chopstick.

510
00:23:47,440 --> 00:23:48,680
A duel.

511
00:23:49,839 --> 00:23:51,599
So cool.

512
00:23:51,599 --> 00:23:52,400
Rise up! Rise up!

513
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:53,440
I believe in you.

514
00:23:53,440 --> 00:23:55,400
Come on! Win this and I'll reward you.

515
00:23:55,400 --> 00:23:57,079
You do your best too.

516
00:23:57,359 --> 00:23:58,240
Actually,

517
00:23:58,799 --> 00:24:01,880
it's just Commander Liao wanting his son,

518
00:24:02,279 --> 00:24:05,359
and Division Commander Chen using Commander Liao's son

519
00:24:05,599 --> 00:24:06,839
to trade for some territory.

520
00:24:07,440 --> 00:24:09,039
That's all there is to it.

521
00:24:11,599 --> 00:24:13,119
Do you take me for a decoration?

522
00:24:13,279 --> 00:24:15,720
You're in cahoots with Division Commander Chen.

523
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:18,519
If he gets it, you're set.

524
00:24:20,240 --> 00:24:21,279
Actually, everyone

525
00:24:21,720 --> 00:24:23,680
has their own agenda.

526
00:24:24,400 --> 00:24:25,359
Why send

527
00:24:25,359 --> 00:24:28,960
thousands of soldiers to their deaths?

528
00:24:29,720 --> 00:24:30,759
If you're men,

529
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:33,079
you should settle it yourselves.

530
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:34,799
That's easy for you to say.

531
00:24:35,279 --> 00:24:38,160
Our Division Commander Chen is a scholar.

532
00:24:38,880 --> 00:24:41,039
You're clearly just bullying him.

533
00:24:52,039 --> 00:24:52,880
I'll do it.

534
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:56,559
I can't stand watching this either.

535
00:24:57,359 --> 00:24:58,359
Liao Guanguan.

536
00:24:58,880 --> 00:24:59,519
Come on.

537
00:25:00,119 --> 00:25:01,599
Let the two of us have a go.

538
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:07,119
Is this the idea you gave the Old man?

539
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:10,640
Old man,

540
00:25:10,640 --> 00:25:12,599
I believe in your strength.

541
00:25:13,119 --> 00:25:14,400
For the sake of your son,

542
00:25:14,759 --> 00:25:15,720
my brother,

543
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:18,119
I'll definitely back you up.

544
00:25:20,759 --> 00:25:22,079
I now announce

545
00:25:23,200 --> 00:25:24,799
the ultimate showdown:

546
00:25:25,279 --> 00:25:26,440
Pole wrestling.

547
00:25:27,039 --> 00:25:28,279
Get ready to start.

548
00:25:28,720 --> 00:25:30,000
If Liao's side wins,

549
00:25:30,400 --> 00:25:31,640
the Chen-Wei side

550
00:25:32,000 --> 00:25:34,200
will unconditionally return Young Master Liao.

551
00:25:34,440 --> 00:25:36,039
If the Chen-Wei side wins,

552
00:25:36,599 --> 00:25:38,799
Liao's side will give up three towns

553
00:25:39,279 --> 00:25:40,559
in exchange for Young Master Liao.

554
00:25:41,680 --> 00:25:44,359
Crossing the line or leaving the carpet is a loss.

555
00:25:48,599 --> 00:25:49,480
Hands on.

556
00:25:54,960 --> 00:25:55,759
Ready.

557
00:25:59,279 --> 00:26:00,039
Begin!

558
00:26:04,640 --> 00:26:08,519
Rise up! Rise up! Rise up!

559
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:11,920
Come on, Commander Liao!

560
00:26:12,400 --> 00:26:13,599
Come on, Commander Wei!

561
00:26:14,680 --> 00:26:17,079
Division Commander Chen, are we just watching them fight?

562
00:26:18,480 --> 00:26:21,079
Rise up! Rise up! Rise up!

563
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:32,799
Come on! Come on! Come on!

564
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:45,079
Commander Liao wins.

565
00:26:45,279 --> 00:26:47,039
Good, good.

566
00:26:49,039 --> 00:26:50,440
According to our agreement,

567
00:26:51,200 --> 00:26:53,319
the Chen and Wei side must unconditionally

568
00:26:53,319 --> 00:26:54,599
return Young Master Liao.

569
00:26:57,079 --> 00:26:59,279
It seems I never agreed from the start

570
00:26:59,720 --> 00:27:01,400
