574
00:27:10,799 --> 00:27:13,559
Several commanders brawling in a brothel.

575
00:27:14,680 --> 00:27:15,759
Who is the joke?

576
00:27:17,240 --> 00:27:17,960
Men!

577
00:27:18,079 --> 00:27:18,799
Get out of the way!

578
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:27,920
