579
00:27:29,680 --> 00:27:31,359
You'll be court-martialed.

580
00:27:33,400 --> 00:27:34,519
Do you see my gun?

581
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:35,880
Back off.

582
00:27:36,839 --> 00:27:37,640
Move.

583
00:27:37,799 --> 00:27:38,480
Move.

584
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:39,720
Division Commander Chen,

585
00:27:40,799 --> 00:27:42,319
my request is actually very simple.

586
00:27:43,039 --> 00:27:44,880
Just release the little brother.

587
00:27:47,640 --> 00:27:50,880
One pull and I'll put a hole right through you.

588
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:51,720
You wouldn't dare.

589
00:27:51,799 --> 00:27:53,119
See if I dare.

590
00:27:53,680 --> 00:27:54,640
Walk me out.

591
00:27:58,200 --> 00:27:58,839
Make way.

592
00:27:58,920 --> 00:27:59,279
Move.

593
00:27:59,279 --> 00:28:00,039
Make way.

594
00:28:03,359 --> 00:28:04,000
Go.

595
00:28:07,799 --> 00:28:08,519
Don't move.

596
00:28:08,799 --> 00:28:09,160
Put it down.

597
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:09,839
Put down the guns.

598
00:28:10,039 --> 00:28:11,079
Let my Commander go.

599
