Why go through all this?

600
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:17,200
We fought, we drank.

601
00:28:18,759 --> 00:28:19,880
You reneged first.

602
00:28:21,119 --> 00:28:21,920
Commander.

603
00:28:23,160 --> 00:28:25,039
Commander, we brought him.

604
00:28:26,359 --> 00:28:27,200
Tell them to let him go.

605
00:28:29,400 --> 00:28:30,160
Let him go.

606
00:28:30,160 --> 00:28:31,000
You release him first.

607
00:28:32,920 --> 00:28:34,039
Release him.

608
00:28:34,720 --> 00:28:36,920
Commander, let's release them together.

609
00:28:37,319 --> 00:28:38,200
Commander.

610
00:28:39,000 --> 00:28:39,920
Your soldiers

611
00:28:40,279 --> 00:28:41,640
aren't listening to you anymore.

612
00:28:41,640 --> 00:28:42,279
You...

613
00:28:43,799 --> 00:28:45,039
I told you to release him!

614
00:28:45,440 --> 00:28:46,000
I...

615
00:28:46,559 --> 00:28:48,000
I said release him!

616
00:28:52,119 --> 00:28:53,240
Come over here, quick!

617
00:28:54,119 --> 00:28:54,759
You...

618
00:28:54,920 --> 00:28:55,680
Young Master Liao.

619
00:28:56,720 --> 00:28:58,440
Come back, quick. We're here to save you.

620
00:28:58,440 --> 00:28:59,160
Come over here.

621
00:29:00,039 --> 00:29:00,759
Hurry up.

622
00:29:06,119 --> 00:29:07,240
You kid, really...

623
00:29:07,240 --> 00:29:07,880
You...

624
00:29:09,440 --> 00:29:10,440
Thank you, Commander.

625
00:29:10,759 --> 00:29:13,000
I still need to trouble you to escort us a bit, Commander.

626
00:29:13,480 --> 00:29:14,319
Tell them

627
00:29:14,640 --> 00:29:16,160
not to follow us.

628
00:29:21,680 --> 00:29:22,359
Put them down.

629
00:29:24,119 --> 00:29:25,240
Go, go, go, hurry.

630
00:29:25,319 --> 00:29:26,000
Put them down.

631
00:29:33,559 --> 00:29:34,440
Is this settled now?

632
00:29:34,880 --> 00:29:35,559
It is.

633
00:29:37,279 --> 00:29:38,200
Brigade Commander Fan,

634
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:40,799
you never intended

635
00:29:41,000 --> 00:29:42,839
to submit to me wholeheartedly from the start.

636
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:44,839
I am a simple man.

637
00:29:45,319 --> 00:29:47,279
Everything must be about honor.

638
00:29:47,839 --> 00:29:49,960
I've fought Division Commander Chen for so many years.

639
00:29:50,319 --> 00:29:51,759
I wouldn't say we're kindred spirits,

640
00:29:52,519 --> 00:29:54,599
but I understand your usual style.

641
00:29:55,960 --> 00:29:57,000
That Staff Officer of yours...

642
00:29:59,440 --> 00:30:00,400
I don't like him.

643
00:30:01,640 --> 00:30:02,400
What a coincidence.

644
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:04,200
I don't like him either.

645
00:30:07,799 --> 00:30:08,880
Thank you, Commander.

646
00:30:09,599 --> 00:30:10,240
Please.
